## Limitations

The findings are limited by the availability of current data and the subjective nature of opinions expressed in forums and discussion platforms. Additionally, the lack of comprehensive statistical data on motorcycle safety and regulations in different regions limits the ability to draw definitive conclusions. Further research, including empirical studies and expert analyses, would provide a more robust understanding of the issue.